  "detailed_description": "<h1>Upcoming Game From This Developer</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/a05d4c4bf9cfcc88d3fb8f895e6a27db.avif?t=1773975319\" width=920 height=430 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2D Horror Multiplayer (2-4 Players).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with friends, run, hide, and survive in this horror twist on a classic Singaporean game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/108765ad64b3df253f2947ad5b5a3f0d.poster.avif?t=1773975319\" width=1170 height=650 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/108765ad64b3df253f2947ad5b5a3f0d.webm?t=1773975319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/108765ad64b3df253f2947ad5b5a3f0d.mp4?t=1773975319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/7622b52112878fe81c568c6e7d8b1b25.avif?t=1773975319\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A curse has been unleashed upon the village. Ah-Dan discovers a lead to the mysteries and horrors behind the curse, digging deeper into the disturbing truth about the dark side of the village. Never wander after sunset, no matter what.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/c63e2d8e1e1559d22aafa2903c9c2f25.poster.avif?t=1773975319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/c63e2d8e1e1559d22aafa2903c9c2f25.webm?t=1773975319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/c63e2d8e1e1559d22aafa2903c9c2f25.mp4?t=1773975319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/9e01380b68003489df05a940429ca6fe.avif?t=1773975319\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>The Not-So-Delicious Food</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/f69593506573d54f44358d162fb762a9.avif?t=1773975319\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/013107147a35858de6e651ab717ff351.avif?t=1773975319\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terrifying Antagonists</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story rich to get you entangled with.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interesting and creepy puzzles around the entire game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Animated Illustrations to disturb you further.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A very atmospheric environment that consists of day and night.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional side stories and hidden lore for you to dig around</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An unlockable gallery.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/288427277288c0705cf5a1998890e3c2.avif?t=1773975319\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi, I'm Justus Yew, the game creator of Before Sunset. Before Sunset is a game inspired by an old village me and my sister used to visit, the hometown of our grandparents. We had one of the best memories there, and creating Before Sunset became a must as a tribute to our childhood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are very excited to finally launch the game. Enjoy!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/7622b52112878fe81c568c6e7d8b1b25.avif?t=1773975319\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A curse has been unleashed upon the village. Ah-Dan discovers a lead to the mysteries and horrors behind the curse, digging deeper into the disturbing truth about the dark side of the village. Never wander after sunset, no matter what.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/c63e2d8e1e1559d22aafa2903c9c2f25.poster.avif?t=1773975319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/c63e2d8e1e1559d22aafa2903c9c2f25.webm?t=1773975319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/c63e2d8e1e1559d22aafa2903c9c2f25.mp4?t=1773975319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/9e01380b68003489df05a940429ca6fe.avif?t=1773975319\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>The Not-So-Delicious Food</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/f69593506573d54f44358d162fb762a9.avif?t=1773975319\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/013107147a35858de6e651ab717ff351.avif?t=1773975319\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terrifying Antagonists</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story rich to get you entangled with.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interesting and creepy puzzles around the entire game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Animated Illustrations to disturb you further.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A very atmospheric environment that consists of day and night.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional side stories and hidden lore for you to dig around</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An unlockable gallery.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980820/extras/288427277288c0705cf5a1998890e3c2.avif?t=1773975319\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi, I'm Justus Yew, the game creator of Before Sunset. Before Sunset is a game inspired by an old village me and my sister used to visit, the hometown of our grandparents. We had one of the best memories there, and creating Before Sunset became a must as a tribute to our childhood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are very excited to finally launch the game. Enjoy!</p>",
